<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Teleop robot</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css"  />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="main">
    <p>Per muovere il robot usa l'analogico, i tasi WASD, le freccette direzionali o un controller</p>
    <p id="waitingconn">Aspettando ricezione video, non teleoperare il robot!</p>
    <video playsinline autoplay muted width="1280" height="720"></video>
    <br/>
    <button id="enable-audio">Abilita audio</button>

    <p id="roomname" style="display: none;">{{roomname}}</p>
    <p id="max_linear" style="display: none;">{{max_linear}}</p>
    <p id="max_angular" style="display: none;">{{max_angular}}</p>
    <p id="max_distance" style="display: none;">{{max_distance}}</p>
    <p id="speedlimiter" style="display: none;">{{speedlimiter}}</p>
    
    <a href="/robotlist" id="linklist">Torna alla lista dei robot</a>

    <span id="logout"><a href="/logout" id="linklogout">Logout</a></span>
    
    </div>
    
    <div id="zone_joystick"></div>

   
    <!--Importo socket.io per le socket, nipplejs per il controller, teleop per mandare i segnali di nipplejs al socket, watch per ricevere streaming webrtc -->
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/nipplejs.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/teleopnipple.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/teleopkeyboard.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/teleopgamepad.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/watch.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/adapter.js"></script>
     <!-- adapter.js serve per rendere piÃ¹ compatibile webrtc con vari browser-->
  </body>
</html>



